Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(208,0)\c&H002A2A2A\bord1.5\blur1\3c&H00FFFFFF\fn方正准圆_GBK\fs30\b1\pos(146.667,65)}本周食谱 {\c&H002B2B2B\3c&H0056C5E8\bord1.5\fs40}馎饦
